Package: figur
Type: Package
Title: Smart Rendering of ggplot and cowplot Objects
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Piotr Tymoszuk
Maintainer: Piotr Tymoszuk <piotr.s.tymoszuk@gmail.com>
Description: Enables custom disc saving and rendering of ggplot objects and multi-plot panels generated by cowplot.
   Keeps together the graphic object, its final dimensions and the final file name.
